Package org.libgit2.jagged

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Branch
    A representation of a git branch, a reference in the refs/heads namespace.
    Capabilities
    A collection of the capabilities offered by libgit2.
    Commit
    Representation of a git commit object.
    DetachedHead
    A pointer to the commit that is the current HEAD commit, which does not correspond to an actual branch.
    GitObject
    Base class for git objects (commits, trees, blobs, etc.)
    ObjectId
    The SHA-1 hash comprising the ID for a git object.
    Options
    Configurable options for libgit2.
    Options.CacheStatistics
    The current statistics for the object cache.
    Reference
    A Reference to another git object.
    Reference.DirectReference
    A DirectReference is a Reference that points immediately to an OID.
    Reference.SymbolicReference
    A SymbolicReference is a Reference to another reference.
    ReferenceCollection
    The references in a repository.
    Repository
    A Repository is the primary interface to a git repository.
    Signature
    The signature of the author or committer of a git object.
    Tree
    A tree represents a folder in a git repository, containing files and subtrees.
    TreeEntry
    A tree entry represents a file or folder in a tree.
    Version
    The version number of Jagged or the underlying libgit2 library.
